{"tid":736733,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"其實對愛情真係唔好抱有一生一世嘅期望","createTime":"2018-07-10T12:27:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-10T14:40:25.000Z","uid":23170,"like":29,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1251495b377223b9ae5a85ae1cfb094a18805a18","tid":736733,"uid":23170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T12:27:41.000Z","msg":"只係簡單咁講，越理想可以一生一世，就越難實現。當你覺得一生一世嘅愛情存在，忘記左所有感情都會有逝去嘅一日，你就會越易將對方嘅存在當做理所當然。<br />\n<br />\n越理解清楚所有嘢喺依個世界都會有終結嘅一日，就會越明白到對方嘅重要性，同珍惜現有嘅重要。所以提醒下自己一切一切都有佢嘅期限，一切一切都會有消逝嘅一日，好好珍惜仲可以共處嘅每一天。。"},{"pid":"acc8f95e16767ae6bdf4b4c1a48b1dcc44f33f0f","tid":736733,"uid":41737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T12:28:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a46c021e60acb4d8e627ceeab45059856868b2a7","tid":736733,"uid":23170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"acc8f95e16767ae6bdf4b4c1a48b1dcc44f33f0f","tid":736733,"uid":41737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T12:28:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T12:28:44.000Z","msg":"人地住公屋唔俾養狗㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a7d69b7b1e6f74bb56b4364f96042de435b2eac","tid":736733,"uid":41737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T12:29:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9c0828befb9a59481ccef3456d43acd2f3239805","tid":736733,"uid":23170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6a7d69b7b1e6f74bb56b4364f96042de435b2eac","tid":736733,"uid":41737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a46c021e60acb4d8e627ceeab45059856868b2a7","tid":736733,"uid":23170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"acc8f95e16767ae6bdf4b4c1a48b1dcc44f33f0f","tid":736733,"uid":41737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T12:28:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T12:28:44.000Z","msg":"人地住公屋唔俾養狗㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018